stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Observed
    Observed --> Protected: protected policy matches
    Observed --> Unknown: insufficient evidence
    Observed --> Candidate: rule evidence matches
    Candidate --> ReportOnly: Phases 0 through 4
    Candidate --> ReviewRequired: contextual or medium/high risk
    Candidate --> MoveCandidate: supported movement is preferable
    Candidate --> SafeCandidate: confirmed low-risk evidence
    ReportOnly --> Stale: newer scan required
    ReviewRequired --> Stale
    MoveCandidate --> Stale
    SafeCandidate --> Stale
    Stale --> NoLongerPresent: target absent on rescan
    Stale --> Observed: refreshed evidence
    Protected --> [*]
    Unknown --> [*]
    NoLongerPresent --> [*]
